quran[89]{c,v,t}:
  43,1,"Haa – Meem. (Mashoko aya ndemamwe ezvishamiso zviri muQur’aan, uye hapana anoziva zvaanoreva kunze kwaAllah)"
  43,2,Ndinopika neGwaro (Qur’aan) riri pachena (Rinobuditsa zvinhu zvese pachena)
  43,3,"Zvirokwazvo, takariita Qur’aan rive muchirudzi chechiArabhu kuti muve munonzwisisa"
  43,4,"Uye zvirokwazvo (Qur’aan) riri muna Amai veBhuku (Al-Lauh Al-Mahfoodh) nesu, zvirokwazvo ndere pamusoro, rizere neungwaru"
  43,5,"Tochitora here yeuchidzo (Qur’aan) kubva kwamuri, nokuda kwekuti muri vanhu vanopfurikidza mwero"
  43,6,Uyezve vaporofita vangani vatakatumira pakati pevanhu vekare
  43,7,Uyezve hakuna kuuya muporofita kwavari kusara kwekuti vaimuseka
  43,8,"Naizvozvo takaparadza vanhu vakasimba pane ava, uye muenzaniso wevekare wakapfuura (Pamberi pavo)"
  43,9,"Uye zvirokwazvo ukavabvunza: “Ndiani akasika matenga nenyika?” Zvirokwazvo, vachataura kuti: “Samasimba vane ruzivo rwose ndivo vakawasika.”"
  43,10,"Avo vakakugadzirirai nyika semubhedha, uye vakakugadzirirai nzira mairi, kuti muve munotungamirirwa (munofamba zvakanaka)"
  43,11,"Uye avo vanotumira mvura (inonaya) kubva kudenga zvakaenzanirana, naizvozvo tinopa upenyu kuivhu nayo mvura, uye saizvozvo muchava munodzoswa (kuupenyu mushure mekunge mafa)"
  43,12,"Uye avo vakasika zvinhu zvose zviri zviviri zviviri (chirume nechikadzi), uye vakakugadzirirai ngarava nezvipfuyo izvo zvamunotasva"
  43,13,"Kuti muve munotasva kumisana yazvo (zvipfuyo), uye kuti muve munorangarira makomborero aTenzi venyu pamunotasva, uye moti: “Kurumbidzwa ngakuve kune avo vakatungamidza izvi kwatiri, uye hataikwanisa kuzviwana (nekuda kwesimba redu)!”"
  43,14,“Uye zvirokwazvo kuna Tenzi vedu tichadzokera!”
  43,15,"Asi vanovasanganisa (Allah) nechidimbu kubva mune vamwe varanda vavo (vachiti vane vana uye vachivaenzanisa pakunamata). Zvirokwazvo, munhu ari mukusatenda kuri pachena"
  43,16,"Kana kuti (Allah) vakatora vanasikana kubva mune zvavakasika, uye ivo (Allah) vakakusarudzirai imi vanakomana"
  43,17,"Uye kana umwe wavo akaudzwa nezvemashoko (ekuzvarwa kwemwanasikana) zvaanotaura kune Mupi wenyasha (Allah), chiso chake chinosviba uye anozadzwa nekutsamwa"
  43,18,"Uyo anokudzwa achishongedzwa (achipfekedzwa siriki negoridhe, mukadzi), uye asingakwanisi pakupokana kutaura mashoko ari pachena"
  43,19,"Uye vanoita ngirozi izvo dziri varanda veMupi ane nyasha (Allah), vakadzi. Vakamboona kusikwa kwazvo here? Uchapupu hwavo hwuchanyorwa uye vachabvunzwa"
  43,20,"Uye vanoti: “Dai kusiri kuda kweMupi ane nyasha (Allah), tingadai tisina kuzvinamata.” Havana ruzivo nazvo, uye hapana chavanoita kusara kwekunyepa"
  43,21,Kana kuti takavapa rimwe Bhuku mushure meiri (Qur’aan) iro ravarikubatisisa
  43,22,"Asi vanoti: “Takawana madzibaba edu vachitevera imwe nzira nechitendero, uye tinozvitungamirira kuburikidza netsoka dzavo.”"
  43,23,"Uye saizvozvo, hatina kutuma muyambiri mushure mako (Muhammad (SAW)) kune guta ripi zvarwo (vanhu), asi vaigara zvakanaka pakati pavo vakati: “Zvirokwazvo, takawana madzibaba edu vachitevera imwe nzira nechitendero, uye zvirokwazvo ticharamba tichitevera tsoka dzavo.”"
  43,24,"(Muyambiri) akati: “Kunyangwe ndakuunzirai gwara rakanaka pane ramakawana madzibaba enyu achitevera?” Vakati: “Zvirokwazvo, hatitendi mune zvawakatumwa nazvo.”"
  43,25,"Naizvozvo takavadzorera (takavaranga), uye tarisai ndeapi akazova magumo eavo vakaramba (Islaam)"
  43,26,"Uye (Rangarira) apo Abrahamu paakati kuna baba vake nevanhu vake: “Zvirokwazvo, handipo pane zvamunonamata.”"
  43,27,"“Kusara kwaivo (Allah) vakandisika; uye zvirokwazvo, vachanditungamirira.”"
  43,28,"Uye akariita shoko (Laa ilaaha illallaah (Hapana chimwe chinhu chine kodzero yekunamatwa kunze kwaAllah)) rinogara muvana vake, uye kuti zvimwe vangadzoke (kuna Allah kana kuwana yambiro)"
  43,29,"Asi ndakapa (zvakanaka zvehupenyu hwuno) kune ava (vasingatendi) nemadzibaba avo kuti vafare, kusvikira chokwadi chauya kwavari (Qur’aan), nemutumwa (Muhammad (SAW)) ari pachena (anoburitsa zvinhu zvese pachena)"
  43,30,"Asi pakauya chokwadi kwavari (Qur’aan), vakati (vasingatendi mariri): “Aya ndiwo mapipi, uye hatitendi maari.”"
  43,31,"Uye vakati: “Sei Qur’aan iri risina kudzikiswa kumurume mukuru wemaguta maviri (Makkah neTaif)?”"
  43,32,"Ndivo here vanopa tsitsi dzaTenzi vako? Tisu tinopa pakati pavo raramo yavo muhupenyu hwepano pasi, uye tinosimudzira vamwe vavo pamusoro pevamwe muzvidanho, kuti vamwe vave vanotora vamwe mumabasa avo. Asi tsitsi dzaTenzi vako (Paradhiso) dziri nani pane zvavanounganidza"
  43,33,"Uye dai vanhu vakanga vari boka rimwe chete (vasingatendi), tingadai takapa vanhu vasingatendi muna Mupi ane nyasha (Allah) matenga esirivha edzimba dzavo, nemanera avanokwira nawo"
  43,34,Uye padzimba dzavo paiva nemisiwo (yesirivha) nemibhedha (yesirivha) yavairarira
  43,35,Uye shongedzo dzegoridhe. Asi zvose izvi hapana zvazviri kusara kwemafaro epano panyika. Uye hupenyu hwuchatevera hwuna Tenzi vako ndewe avo vanotya Allah (vanoteerera Allah)
  43,36,"Uye uyo anofuratira kubva kurangariro yeMupi ane nyasha (Allah) (Qur’aan nekunamata Allah), tinomusarudzira Satani kuti ave shamwari yake"
  43,37,"Uye zvirokwazvo vanasatani vanovadzivirira kubva munzira (yaAllah), asi vanofunga kuti vakatungamiririrwa"
  43,38,"Kusvika (iye) auya kwatiri, anoti (kushamwari yake satani): “Ndinoshuvira kuti dai pakati pangu newe pange pane musiyano wemufambo wemabvazuva maviri (kana wemabvazuva nemadokero).” Zvirokwazvo uri shamwari yakaipa"
  43,39,Hazvikubatsirei zuva ranhasi (imi vasingatendi) nekuti maiita zvakaipa. Muchava vagovani (iwe neshamwari yako) mumarwadzo
  43,40,"Muhammad (SAW)) ungaite kuti matsi anzwe here, kana kutungamirira bofu, kana uyo ari mukurasika kuri pachena"
  43,41,"Uye kunyangwe tikakutora (Muhammad (SAW)), zvirokwazvo tichava tinovadzorera (tinovaranga)"
  43,42,"Kana (tikava) tinokuratidza zvatakavavimbisa, zvirokwazvo tine simba pamusoro pavo"
  43,43,"Naizvozvo batisisa (Muhammad (SAW)) izvo zvirikudzikiswa kwauri. Zvirokwazvo, uri panzira yakaswatuka"
  43,44,"Uye zvirokwazvo (Qur’aan) iri zvirokwazvo iyambiro kwauri (Muhammad (SAW)) nevanhu vako, uye muchabvunzwa (nezvaro)"
  43,45,"Uye (Muhammad (SAW)) bvunza vamwe vevatumwa vedu vatakatuma mushure mako kuti: “Takasarudza here vamwe vanamwari kuti vave vanonamatwa kunze kweMupi ane nyasha (Allah)?”"
  43,46,"Uye zvirokwazvo takatuma Musa nezviratidzo zvedu kuna Farawo nemadzimambo ake (achivakoka kuchitendero chaAllah cheIslaam). Akati: “Zvirokwazvo, ndiri mutumwa waTenzi vepasi rose (vanhu nemaJinn nezvihnu zvese).”"
  43,47,"Asi apo paakasvika kwavari nezviratidzo zvedu kwavari, zvirokwazvo vakazviseka"
  43,48,"Uye hapana chiratidzo chatakavaratidza asi kuti chaiva chikuru kudarika chimwe chacho, uye takavabata nemarwadzo kuti pamwe vangadzoke (kuchitendero chaAllah, Islaam)"
  43,49,"Uye vakati (kuna Musa): “Iwe wemapipi! Tikumbirire kuna Tenzi vako maererano nezvavakakuvimbisa. Zvirokwazvo, tichava tinozvitungamirira (zvakanaka).”"
  43,50,"Asi patakabvisa mutongo kwavari, vakave vanotyora chitsidzo (kuti vaizotenda tikabvisa marwadzo kubva kwavari)"
  43,51,"Uye Farawo akasheedzera kuvanhu vake (achiti): “Imi vanhu vangu! Hausi hwangu here humambo hweEgypt, uye nzizi idzi dzinoyerera pasi pangu? Hamuoni here?”"
  43,52,"“Handisi nani here pane uyu (Musa) wepasi, uye asingagoni kutaura zvinonzwika?”"
  43,53,"“Sei nguwo dzendarama dzisina kuiswa paari, kana kutumwa aine ngirozi?”"
  43,54,"Naizvozvo (Farawo) akafurira vanhu vake uye vakamuteerera. Zvirokwazvo, vange vari vanhu vakapanduka (vasingateereri Allah)"
  43,55,"Naizvozvo pavakatitsamwisa, takavapa murango, uye tikavanyudza vose"
  43,56,Uye takavaita chidzidzo uye muenzaniso kune vaizotevera
  43,57,"Uye panotorwa mwanakomana waMariya (Jesu) somuenzaniso, vanhu vako vanoseka muenzaniso iwowo"
  43,58,"Uye vanoti: “Vanamwari vedu vari nani here kana kuti iye (Jesu)?” Havape muenzaniso uyu, kusara kwekuda kupikisa. Naizvozvo vari vanhu vanopikisa"
  43,59,"Zvirokwazvo, (Isa (Jesu)) anga asiri kunze kwemuranda. Takamupa makomborero edu, uye tikamuita muenzaniso kuvana vaIzirairi (kusikwa kwake pasina baba)"
  43,60,"Uye dai taida, ingadai (takakuparadzai imi vanhu mese, uye) tikaisa ngirozi pachinzvimbo chenyu panyika"
  43,61,Uye iye (Isa (Jesu)) mwanakomana waMariya (nekuburuka kwake achibva kudenga achiuya pasi pano) achave chiratidzo chinozivikanwa chenguva (zuva rekutongwa). Naizvozvo musave nefungidziro pamusoro paro (zuva rekutongwa). Uye nditeverei (ini Allah)! Iri ndiro gwara rakatwasuka (Islaam)
  43,62,"Uye musave munosiya Satani achikurasisai (kubva muchitendero cheIslaam). Zvirokwazvo, (satani) muvengi ari pachena kwamuri"
  43,63,"Uye Isa (Jesu) paakauya nehumboo huri pachena akati: “Zvirokwazvo, ndave ndinouya kwamuri neAl-Hikmah ( Huporofita), uye kuti ndive ndinoburitsa pachena izvo zvamaisiyana. Naizvozvo ityai Allah uye mova munonditeerera.”"
  43,64,"“Zvirokwazvo, Allah ndi Tenzi vangu uye Tenzi venyu. Naizvozvo vanamatei. Iri ndiro gwara rakatwasuka (Islaam).”"
  43,65,Asi mapato pakati pavo akapatsanurana. Nokudaro matambudziko kune avo vanokanganisa (nekutaura manyepo pamusoro paJesu) kubva kune mutongo wakaomarara unorwadza
  43,66,Vanomirira here nguva ichauya nekukurumidza kwavari vasingazive
  43,67,"Shamwari pazuva iri dzichave vavengi, kusara kwevaitya (Allah)"
  43,68,"(Zvichanzi kune avo vaitenda): Vanamati vangu! Hapana kutya kuchave kwamuri zuva ranhasi, kana kuti kusuruvara"
  43,69,Avo vaitenda muzviratidzo zvedu uye vaive vakazvipira kuna Allah (maMuslim)
  43,70,Pindai muParadhiso imi nevakadzi venyu murufaro
  43,71,"Matireyi egoridhe nemakomichi achatenderedzwa mavari. Mariri (Paradhiso) muchange muine zvinoshuvirwa nemoyo yavo, neizvo meso anoyevedzwa nazvo, uye vachagaramo zvachose"
  43,72,Iri ndiro Paradhiso ramagadzwa nhaka nekuda kwemabasa enyu amaiita (pahupenyu hwepanyika)
  43,73,Mariri (Paradhiso) kwamuri muchange muine michero yakawanda yamuchange muchidya (sezvamunoshuvira)
  43,74,"Zvirokwazo, maMujrimoon (vatadzi) vachange vari mumarwadzo ekumoto umo mavachagara zvachose"
  43,75,"Marwadzo haazomborerutswi kwavari, uye vachakandwa mumatambudziko vaine kudemba kwakanyanya, uye vaine kushushikana mariri"
  43,76,"Hatina kuva tinovakanganisira, asi (kuti) ivo pachavo vaiva vatadzi"
  43,77,"Uye vachachema: “Iwe Malik (muchengetedzi weGehena)! Ita kuti Tenzi vako vatipedzise (vatiuraye).” Achati: “Zvirokwazvo, muchagaramo zvachose.”"
  43,78,"Zvirokwazvo, taunza chokwadi (Muhammad (SAW) neQur’aan) kwamuri, asi vazhinji venyu vanovenga chokwadi"
  43,79,Kana kuti vakaronga urongwa? Naizvozvo nesuwo tiri kuronga
  43,80,"Kana kuti vanofunga here kuti hatinzwi zvakavandika zvavo uye zvavanoutaura muchivande? Hongu (tinozinzwa), uye vatumwa vedu (ngirozi) vanawo, vachinyora"
  43,81,"Iti (Muhammad (SAW)): “Kana vane nyasha dzose (Allah) vaine mwana (kana vana sezvamunotaura), naizvozvo ndiri wekutanga weavo vanomunamata (kuramba zvamunotaura, uye kutenda kuti Allah vari vega uye havana vana).”"
  43,82,"Kukudzwa kwose ngakuve kuna Tenzi vematenga nenyika, Tenzi vechigaro chepamusoro-soro. Kurumbidzwa kwose ngakuve kwavari pane zvose zvavanovasanganisa navo"
  43,83,Saka vasiyei vachitaura zvisina maturo uye vachitamba kusvikira vasangana nezuva ravo iro ravakavimbiswa
  43,84,"Ndivo (Allah) vanova vamwechete Ilaah (Mwari vanofanirwa kunamatwa) kudenga, vanova zvakare Ilaah (Mwari vanofanirwa kunamatwa) panyika. Ndivo vazere neungwaru, muzivi wezvose"
  43,85,"Makomborero ndeavo, muridzi weumambo hwekudenga nepasi, nezvose zviri pakati pawo, uye kwavari ndiko kune ruzivo rwenguva, uye kwavari muchadzoserwa (mese)"
  43,86,"Uye avo vavanodana kunze kwavo (Allah) havana masimba ekumiririra – kusara kweavo vanopa uchapupu pachokwadi (vanotenda muhumwechete hwaAllah uye vachiteerera mirairo yavo), uye vanoziva (humwechete hwaAllah)"
  43,87,"Asi kana ukavabvunza kuti ndiani akavasika, muzvokwadi vanoti: “Allah.” Saka vanofuratira sei (mukunamata Allah vakavasika)"
  43,88,"(Uye Allah vane ruzivo) rwe (Mashoko aMuhammad (SAW)) anoti: “Tenzi wangu! Zvirokwazvo, ava vanhu vasingatendi!”"
  43,89,"Saka vafuratire (Muhammad (SAW)) uye oti: Salaam (Runyararo)! Asi vachazviziva"